  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Daily buffet breakfast with hot option</li>
<li><strong>Free</strong> packed lunches†</li>
<li><strong>Free</strong> afternoon tea &amp; freshly baked cake†</li>
<li>5 course evening meals with a choice of menu plus vegetarian option†</li>
<li>Pre-dinner apéritif, choice of complimentary wines throughout dinner, tea/coffee &amp; chocolates†</li>
<li>Weekly barbeque or Al Fresco meal (weather permitting)</li>
<li><strong>Free</strong> tea and coffee throughout the day</li>
<li>Friendly service from your Inghams Chalet Hotel team</li>
</ul>
<p>†Chalet Hotel staff have one day off per week, so dinner is 6 evenings per week; packed lunch &amp; afternoon tea are 5 days per week. For more info on chalet, Chalet Hotels and 'Half-Board Plus' arrangements <a href="/{localLink:bb7c343b-44f3-4f8e-a79c-f289eac4a027}" title="Chalet Hotels">click here</a> &gt;</p>]]></cateringDescription>
