  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>New for Summer 2014</strong>, Chalet Hotel Valverde is an exciting addition to our Italian programme, and is sure to prove a popular next choice for guests who have already enjoyed its sister property, <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="/{localLink:63bd78b8-e3cf-4dc9-932a-1cdfa5346308}" target="_blank" title="NEW Chalet Hotel Valverde">Chalet Hotel Al Pigher</a> in <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="/{localLink:2aa7eb53-9139-463f-bfa2-0d64f75b5a72}" target="_blank" title="La Villa">La Villa</a>.</p>
<p>Its prime location, literally next door to the Punta Jolanda chairlift, makes the Valverde ideal for keen walkers, bringing many of the most popular walking trails within reach of a swift and comfortable uphill ride!</p>
<p>Our friendly and professional Inghams Chalet Hotel team ensure a relaxed and informal ambience in this good quality accommodation, with its welcoming facilities, excellent cuisine, and outstanding value for money.</p>
<p>Whether you are looking for an active walking holiday or a slower paced 'get away from it all' stay amidst splendidly scenic surroundings, you will find everything you need here at Chalet Hotel Valverde in Gressoney.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
